<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>אימות סיסמה להפקת Gate Pass</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f6fa;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      direction: rtl;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #d0d7de;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #003f8a;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .card input[type="password"] {
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background-color: #f9fbfd;
      color: #1e1e1e;
    }

    .card button {
      background-color: #003f8a;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .card button:hover {
      background-color: #0050cc;
    }

    .error-message {
      color: #c62828;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>הנהג מוגדר כמנוע</h1>
    <p>יש להזין סיסמת מנהל לצורך הפקת Gate Pass</p>

    <% if (errorMessage) { %>
      <div class="error-message"><%= errorMessage %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/driver/<%= driverId %>/gatepass" method="POST">
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="הזן סיסמה...">
      <button type="submit">אישור והמשך</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
